# Copy to `.dev.vars` for local development (`wrangler dev` loads it automatically).
# In production, set these with: wrangler secret put GEMINI_API_KEY   (etc.)

# REQUIRED — Google Gemini API key (https://aistudio.google.com/apikey)
GEMINI_API_KEY=""

# OPTIONAL — extra market-data providers (used as fallbacks when set).
# The platform works keyless out of the box (Binance for crypto, Yahoo for everything else).
FINNHUB_API_KEY=""
ALPHAVANTAGE_API_KEY=""
POLYGON_API_KEY=""
COINGECKO_API_KEY=""
